      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$5,900 - Honest project classic with plenty of potential for the right buyer. This one is not a turn-key car and will need significant cosmetic and mechanical attention, but it\u2019s a complete-looking candidate with vintage appeal and a solid starting point for restoration, rebuilding, or parts use. Best suited for someone who knows what they\u2019re getting into and wants an affordable entry into a classic project.",
