      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for the right buyer. It shows its age and will benefit from attention, but it offers a low-cost entry point for someone seeking basic transportation, a starter project, or a value-focused purchase. A sensible choice for buyers who appreciate honest condition and room to improve.",
      "price": 4900.0,
